.TH SINGINE-XML 1 "2026-03-13" "singine 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
singine-xml \- generate XML request, response, and heatmap artifacts
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine xml matrix
[\fB--db\fR \fIPATH\fR] [\fB--output-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Runs built-in and discovered scenarios across SQL, SPARQL, and GraphQL query
dimensions and writes XML artifacts that summarize request inputs, response
cells, and heatmap scoring.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --db \fIPATH\fR
SQLite bridge database to query. Default is
.IR /tmp/sqlite.db .
.TP
.B --output-dir \fIPATH\fR
Destination directory for
.IR request.xml ,
.IR response.xml ,
and
.IR heatmap.xml .
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
singine xml matrix
singine xml matrix --db /tmp/sqlite.db --output-dir /tmp/singine-xml-matrix
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR singine (1),
.BR singine-bridge (1)
